dgs6600EquipmentMIB.name: dgs6600EquipmentMIB
dgs6600EquipmentMIB.description: The structure of chassis HW function for the proprietary enterprise.

chassisControlModuleLEDInfoIndex.name: chassisControlModuleLEDInfoIndex
chassisControlModuleLEDInfoIndex.description: This object indicates the slot index of Control Module.

chassisControlModuleLEDInfoConsole.name: chassisControlModuleLEDInfoConsole
chassisControlModuleLEDInfoConsole.description: This object indicates the console type. There are two different interfaces: 1: RS232. 2: USB.

chassisControlModuleLEDInfoMaster.name: chassisControlModuleLEDInfoMaster
chassisControlModuleLEDInfoMaster.description: This object indicates whether this control module is master or not? 1: This control module is active CM. 2: This control module is standby CM.

chassisControlModuleLEDInfoCPUUtilizatio.name: chassisControlModuleLEDInfoCPUUtilization
chassisControlModuleLEDInfoCPUUtilizatio.description: This object indicates the CPU utilization(in percentage) of this control module.

chassisControlModuleLEDInfoMgmtPortStatu.name: chassisControlModuleLEDInfoMgmtPortStatus
chassisControlModuleLEDInfoMgmtPortStatu.description: This object indicates the management port status.

chassisControlModuleLEDInfoMgmtPortSpeed.name: chassisControlModuleLEDInfoMgmtPortSpeed
chassisControlModuleLEDInfoMgmtPortSpeed.description: This object indicates the management port link speed.

chassisPowerIndex.name: chassisPowerIndex
chassisPowerIndex.description: This object indicates the PSU index.

chassisPowerExist.name: chassisPowerExist
chassisPowerExist.description: This object indicates whether the specified PSU is exist or not. 1: The PSU is not exist. 2: The PSU is installed.

chassisPowerType.name: chassisPowerType
chassisPowerType.description: This object indicates the PSU type. 1: The PSU type is AC. 2: The PSU type is DC. 3: The PSU type is unknown.

chassisPowerAlive.name: chassisPowerAlive
chassisPowerAlive.description: This object indicates whether the specified PSU is alive or not. 1: The PSU is not available. 2: The PSU is working normally.

chassisPowerVoltage.name: chassisPowerVoltage
chassisPowerVoltage.description: This object indicates the output voltage(V) of the specified PSU.

chassisPowerCurrent.name: chassisPowerCurrent
chassisPowerCurrent.description: This object indicates the output current(mA) of the specified PSU.

chassisPowerPowerWatt.name: chassisPowerPowerWatt
chassisPowerPowerWatt.description: This object indicates the output power(W) of the specified PSU.

chassisPowerFanSpeed.name: chassisPowerFanSpeed
chassisPowerFanSpeed.description: This object indicates the internal fan speed(rpm) of specified PSU.

chassisFanTrayInfoState.name: chassisFanTrayInfoState
chassisFanTrayInfoState.description: This object indicates the fan tray state. There are three different state: 1. Not existed 2. Existed but failed 3. Working normally

chassisFanIndex.name: chassisFanIndex
chassisFanIndex.description: This object indicates the fan tray index.

chassisFanStatus.name: chassisFanStatus
chassisFanStatus.description: This object indicates the fan status(ok or failed).

chassisFanSpeed.name: chassisFanSpeed
chassisFanSpeed.description: This object indicates the fan speed in RPM.

chassisSlotIndex.name: chassisSlotIndex
chassisSlotIndex.description: This object indicates the slot index.

chassisSlotState.name: chassisSlotState
chassisSlotState.description: This object indicates the slot state: 1: The slot has no card installed. 2: The card which installed at this slot is not powered up. 3: The card which installed at this slot is failed. 4: The card which installed at this slot is booting up. 5: The card is powered up.

chassisSlotLEDPoEModeEnabled.name: chassisSlotLEDPoEModeEnabled
chassisSlotLEDPoEModeEnabled.description: This object indicates whether the PoE mode is enabled or not?

chassisSlotModel.name: chassisSlotModel
chassisSlotModel.description: This object indicates the card model name.

chassisSlotSerialNumber.name: chassisSlotSerialNumber
chassisSlotSerialNumber.description: This object indicates the serial number of the installed card.

chassisSlotHwVersion.name: chassisSlotHwVersion
chassisSlotHwVersion.description: This object indicates the HW version of the installed card.

chassisSlotPCBAVersion.name: chassisSlotPCBAVersion
chassisSlotPCBAVersion.description: This object indicates the PCBA version of the installed card.

chassisSlotBootloaderVersion.name: chassisSlotBootloaderVersion
chassisSlotBootloaderVersion.description: This object indicates the PCBA version of the installed card.

chassisSlotRuntimeVersion.name: chassisSlotRuntimeVersion
chassisSlotRuntimeVersion.description: This object indicates the runtime version of the installed card.

chassisSlotCPLDVersion.name: chassisSlotCPLDVersion
chassisSlotCPLDVersion.description: This object indicates the CPLD version of the installed card.

chassisSlotFirsMacAddress.name: chassisSlotFirsMacAddress
chassisSlotFirsMacAddress.description: This object indicates the first MAC address of the installed card.

chassisSlotNumberOfMacAddress.name: chassisSlotNumberOfMacAddress
chassisSlotNumberOfMacAddress.description: This object indicates the number of MAC address of the installed card.

chassisTemperatureSlotIndex.name: chassisTemperatureSlotIndex
chassisTemperatureSlotIndex.description: This object indicates the slot number which is currently querying.

chassisTemperatureInletCurrent.name: chassisTemperatureInletCurrent
chassisTemperatureInletCurrent.description: This object displays the current temperature of Inlet sensor.

chassisTemperatureInletOverheat.name: chassisTemperatureInletOverheat
chassisTemperatureInletOverheat.description: This object displays the overheat threshold of Inlet sensor.

chassisTemperatureInletHeatdown.name: chassisTemperatureInletHeatdown
chassisTemperatureInletHeatdown.description: This object displays the heatdown threshold of Inlet sensor.

chassisTemperatureCenterCurrent.name: chassisTemperatureCenterCurrent
chassisTemperatureCenterCurrent.description: This object displays the current temperature of Center sensor.

chassisTemperatureCenterOverheat.name: chassisTemperatureCenterOverheat
chassisTemperatureCenterOverheat.description: This object displays the overheat threshold of Center sensor.

chassisTemperatureCenterHeatdown.name: chassisTemperatureCenterHeatdown
chassisTemperatureCenterHeatdown.description: This object displays the heatdown threshold of Center sensor.

chassisTemperatureOutletCurrent.name: chassisTemperatureOutletCurrent
chassisTemperatureOutletCurrent.description: This object displays the current temperature of Outlet sensor. The string N/A will be displayed to indicate that the card has no this sensor.

chassisTemperatureOutletOverheat.name: chassisTemperatureOutletOverheat
chassisTemperatureOutletOverheat.description: This object displays the overheat threshold of Outlet sensor. The string N/A will be displayed to indicate that the card has no this sensor.

chassisTemperatureOutletHeatdown.name: chassisTemperatureOutletHeatdown
chassisTemperatureOutletHeatdown.description: This object displays the outlet threshold of Outlet sensor. The string N/A will be displayed to indicate that the card has no this sensor.

chassisPortLEDIFIndex.name: chassisPortLEDIFIndex
chassisPortLEDIFIndex.description: This object indicates the interface index.

chassisPortLEDIFName.name: chassisPortLEDIFName
chassisPortLEDIFName.description: This object indicates the interface name.

chassisPortLEDStatus.name: chassisPortLEDStatus
chassisPortLEDStatus.description: This object indicates the port LED status: 1: The port LED status of the interface index is off. 2: The port LED status of the interface index is steady-amber. 3: The port LED status of the interface index is steady-green. 4: The port LED status of the interface index is blinking-amber. 5: The port LED status of the interface index is blinking-green.

chassisPortLEDMode.name: chassisPortLEDMode
chassisPortLEDMode.description: This object indicates the port LED mode: 1: The port LED is in Ethernet mode. 2: The poer LED is in PoE mode.

chassisPortLEDMediumType.name: chassisPortLEDMediumType
chassisPortLEDMediumType.description: This object indicates the port LED medium type: 1: The medium type of port LED is copper. 2: The medium type of port LED is fiber.
